{"tid":432493,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"OnePlus 被揭收集大量用戶資料","createTime":"2017-10-11T14:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T17:38:00.000Z","uid":30169,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb3282bc3952de22ced00e5f2e7d71d95213e1b","tid":432493,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4988/209256/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4988%2F209256%2F1%2F&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=697453a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4988/209256/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n虎仔(uniqlo) 2017-10-11 12:26<br />\n<br />\n很多公司都會在 Hang 機或系統出問題時，收集和傳送系統資訊，目的是完善系統。什麼是合適的數量每個用戶的想法不同，最近一名軟件工程師 Christopher Moore 就發現，OnePlus 收集大量用戶資料，並且傳送至 OnePlus 的伺服器。<br />\n<br />\nOnePlus 被揭收集大量用戶資料<br />\n<br />\nMoore 在個人網誌公開了他的發現，透過 OWASP ZAP 根據截取他的 OnePlus 2 手機傳送和接收的互聯網流量，除了正常的網絡活動，他還發現大量來自 <a href=\"http://open.oneplus.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fopen.oneplus.net&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=4342e057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">open.oneplus.net</a> 的連線請求。經過深入檢查，Moore 發現網站屬於 OnePlus 並寄存在 Amazon AWS，他的手機恆常地將數據透過 HTTPS 傳送到 <a href=\"http://open.oneplus.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fopen.oneplus.net&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=4342e057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">open.oneplus.net</a> 伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n利用手機內的認證密鑰，Moore 成功將傳送的數據解密，原來他的 OnePlus 2 將每次解鎖、上鎖和意外重啟的時間傳送出去。為了修正系統問題，記錄意外重啟可算合情合理，但監測用戶每次解鎖上鎖的時間就似乎有點超過。Moore 進一步監察了一段時間，得到了更驚人的發現。傳送出去的資料還包括手機的 IMEI 號碼、手機號碼、MAC 地址、電訊網絡名字和 IMSI 號碼、Wi-Fi 連線資料和手機序號，就連每一次用戶打開哪個手機 App，OnePlus 通通都知道。<br />\n<br />\n網站 Android Police 就事件向 OnePlus 查詢，得到的回覆是他們會傳送兩組數據到 Amazon 伺服器，第一組收集的是用戶使用數據，用作因應他們的習慣修正軟件。第二組是手機資訊，用作提供更佳的售後服務。OnePlus 表示第一組數據可以在 Settings &gt; Advanced &gt; Join user experience program 中刪除。有網民發現利用 ADB 根據可以將 OnePlus System Service 徹底移除，不過這軟件跟 Device Manager 連結，移除後或對手機的功能有所影響。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Android Police"},{"pid":"1d73d82855fff69fa091863c4b8147b921b70160","tid":432493,"uid":89199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8c35a385253c4872e27ec0a1a9078b60fe434e3","tid":432493,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"d82a16cdd63e332963d531843c9c0a7083ef9ef2","tid":432493,"uid":39698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"唔意外"},{"pid":"71e407ebff857df697d814207131f3fc8b5aa3fc","tid":432493,"uid":6195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:31:38.000Z","msg":"留名等軟飯王入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e67b0f010904d1550ed356bc89f615fbc55740","tid":432493,"uid":92265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69592067c2f2ad4eecddd14ac8c7403194d39473","tid":432493,"uid":16904,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"唉，an機"},{"pid":"608f0ff07b9df49288c6b2b230e8cc6162c5a4ae","tid":432493,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T18:41:03.000Z","msg":"又話one plus 無後門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5bf508e41366d305fd63943a69a5652b29be1db","tid":432493,"uid":47027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T19:06:22.000Z","msg":"係叫班推oneplus嘅柒頭情何以憾呢？"},{"pid":"1117e1162c04848cc2fa569539564d7f584b2070","tid":432493,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T20:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hk