br />\n<br />\napple仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舉個例？任何一單都得</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT203033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT203033&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6ae3f2ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT203033</a></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/104255_c26be60cfd1ba40772b5ac48b95ab19b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F104255_c26be60cfd1ba40772b5ac48b95ab19b.png&h=2e55e151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成堆service都係upload data返去apple個server<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲未計你其他apps</blockquote><br />\n其實Apple全部做之前都有問你.<br />\n無用過ios?</blockquote><br />\n其實你買機開通service前有份license term有寫,只係無人有心機睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係指佢需要你開放會再問你一次"},{"pid":"b89d54c72b908157bf48fd74a9f4d63b6fe91d89","tid":432493,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:50:29.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n根本係大陸機問題<br />\n俾你ios開放俾大陸一樣都收集你資料<br />\n邊個反共就捉邊個"},{"pid":"656a280e5bf81b98ce007dc62af96cdf33b652d6","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話oneplus乾淨冇後門既</blockquote><br />\n之前未搵到所以無，而家搵到所以有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b8b8f959281c992c4f9b82e95e6f8810263b2a","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:52:41.000Z","msg":"oppo plus真係支那人先會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3102381b06a9e43830ff310f30e4243d4ff2fe24","tid":432493,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"apple 咪一撚樣<br />\n<br />\n一單棱鏡計劃已經露晒底"},{"pid":"f05e012abc22b0cf1f04e630db50353d1330f5ca","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"臭蟲論支那人<br />\n你用非支那機屌侵侵，美國政府都唔會理你<br />\n你試下用支那機屌習近平，你最好呢一世都唔好出境又或者唔好行近西九/西環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412692097153c586bd1204e90ee1cd0493d46242","tid":432493,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小題大造 根本每一部機都會收集電話數據 <br />\n<br />\napple仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舉個例？任何一單都得</blockquote><br />\n我舉個例啦，碌柒比三叔強制鎖機，等你用都無得用，迫你退機。好啦退啦，唔好意思，香港不包括係全球之列，有問題請到外太空處理。</blockquote><br />\n舉android 我驚爆post都未舉完</blockquote><br />\n你唔好俾佢哋轉移視線狂打稻香人<br />\n佢哋想蒙糊焦點，將自身有嘅問題推到所有機都有，用嚟合理化自己嘅做法<br />\n正如支那會監控異見人士，班支那人就話美國都有，但明明性質完全唔同，支那係接維權律師、反共港台人士、學運領袖，美國係針對恐怖份子、黑幫，係唔會捉異見人士，但支那人就會將兩樣嘢放埋一齊地圖炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為美國無派鬼妹幫人洗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cfb04e593b047b048483784f3ede59f77481d8","tid":432493,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n根本係大陸機問題<br />\n俾你ios開放俾大陸一樣都收集你資料<br />\n邊個反共就捉邊個</blockquote><br />\n中共就指明要apple將中國iuser 嘅資料放係貴州新起個center, apple 都係照做。<br />\n呢個係擺明嘅事實，不過打手唔該唔好混淆視聽，香港id唔使放係貴州，如果要屈毛，請提供sources"},{"pid":"b4ad7870ff07a10e2638cb676dbcb7330355cecd","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小題大造 根本每一部機都會收集電話數據 <br />\n<br />\napple仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舉個例？任何一單都得</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT203033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT203033&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6ae3f2ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT203033</a></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/104255_c26be60cfd1ba40772b5ac48b95ab19b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F104255_c26be60cfd1ba40772b5ac48b95ab19b.png&h=2e55e151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成堆service都係upload data返去apple個server<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲未計你其他apps</blockquote><br />\n其實Apple全部做之前都有問你.<br />\n無用過ios?</blockquote><br />\n其實你買機開通service前有份license term有寫,只係無人有心機睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係指佢需要你開放會再問你一次</blockquote><br />\n你有冇留意<br />\n本身係講緊oppo plus嘅問題，而家轉移到屌apple而唔講oppo plus嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5286f765ae09d3e927451112bc81a2ff42ac7808","tid":432493,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌<br />\n根本係大陸機問題<br />\n俾你ios開放俾大陸一樣都收集你資料<br />\n邊個反共就捉邊個</blockquote><br />\n中共就指明要apple將中國iuser 嘅資料放係貴州新起個center, apple 都係照做。<br />\n呢個係擺明嘅事實，不過打手唔該唔好混淆視聽，香港id唔使放係貴州，如果要屈毛，請提供sources</blockquote><br />\n果個係支那法律限制，所有大陸賣既an機都唔會有例外"},{"pid":"ca99aaeefdf2686b4401ab1a4080913b42fc69cc","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌<br />\n根本係大陸機問題<br />\n俾你ios開放俾大陸一樣都收集你資料<br />\n邊個反共就捉邊個</blockquote><br />\n中共就指明要apple將中國iuser 嘅資料放係貴州新起個center, apple 都係照做。<br />\n呢個係擺明嘅事實，不過打手唔該唔好混淆視聽，香港id唔使放係貴州，如果要屈毛，請提供sources</blockquote><br />\n果個係支那法律限制，所有大陸賣既an機都唔會有例外</blockquote><br />\n唔好再落搭啦<br />\n佢哋提apple都係想你去幫apple辯護而唔再講oppo plus<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbb534b2cc2691d60833c466bb0d91cffb23c4d","tid":432493,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小題大造 根本每一部機都會收集電話數據 <br />\n<br />\napple仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舉個例？任何一單都得</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT203033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT203033&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6ae3f2ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT203033</a></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢想話, Apple 既機都會收集你數據.<br />\n<br />\nOnePlus 被踢爆 (真係爆, 唔係踢脹)<br />\n<br />\nOnePlus 2 將每次解鎖、上鎖和意外重啟的時間傳送出去。為了修正系統問題，記錄意外重啟可算合情合理，但監測用戶每次解鎖上鎖的時間就似乎有點超過。Moore 進一步監察了一段時間，得到了更<span style=\"color: red;\">驚人的發現</span>。傳送出去的資料還包括<span style=\"color: red;\">手機的 IMEI 號碼</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">手機號碼</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">MAC 地址</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">電訊網絡名字</span>和 <span style=\"color: red;\">IMSI 號碼</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">Wi-Fi 連線資料</span>和<span style=\"color: red;\">手機序號</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">就連每一次用戶打開哪個手機 App</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">OnePlus 通通都知道</span>。<br />\n<br />\n佢果篇廢文係想講蘋果會收集你 location, 但係人地係 Location Data.  再分比 App 用 - 例如 Google Map, wechat, 等要知你係邊既 app.<br />\n<br />\n想知蘋果收集 D 咩消毒, 就應該搵最新既 Link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/au/legal/privacy/en-ww/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fau%2Flegal%2Fprivacy%2Fen-ww%2F&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=68ed3cd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/au/legal/privacy/en-ww/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>What<span style=\"color: red;\"> personal </span>information we collect</strong><br />\n<br />\nWhen you create an Apple ID, apply for commercial credit, purchase a product, download a software update, register for a class at an Apple Retail Store, contact us or participate in an online survey, we may collect a variety of information, including y<span style=\"color: red;\">our name</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">mailing address</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">phone number</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">email address</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">contact preferences</span>, and <span style=\"color: red;\">credit card information</span>.<br />\n<br />\nWhen you share your content with family and friends using Apple products, send gift certificates and products, or invite others to participate in Apple services or forums, Apple may collect the information you provide about those people such as name, mailing address, email address, and phone number. Apple will use such information to fulfill your requests, provide the relevant product or service, or for anti-fraud purposes.<br />\n<br />\nIn certain jurisdictions, we may ask for a government issued ID in limited circumstances including when setting up a wireless account and activating your device, for the purpose of extending commercial credit, managing reservations, or as required by law.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Collection and Use of <span style=\"color: green;\">Non-Personal Information</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nWe also collect data in a form that does not, on its own, permit direct association with any specific individual. We may collect, use, transfer, and disclose non-personal information for any purpose. The following are some examples of non-personal information that we collect and how we may use it:<br />\n<br />\nWe may collect information such as occupation, language, zip code, area code, unique device identifier, referrer URL, location, and the time zone where an Apple product is used so that we can better understand customer behavior and improve our products, services, and advertising.<br />\n<br />\n太長唔想再 Quote, 不過呢, 係咪等如 One Plus 做得岩呢? <br />\n你覺得岩你咪繼續用囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我凈係知道蘋果搞到比人告<br />\n<br />\n拒幫FBI解鎖庫克：不讓步| 蘋果日報<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20160226/37081191/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Fappledaily%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20160226%2F37081191%2F&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=50ac1763\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20160226/37081191/</a><br />\n<br />\n人地一樣有 Report<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/privacy/transparency-reports/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fprivacy%2Ftransparency-reports%2F&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a2ec68ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/privacy/transparency-reports/</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 都有 Report<br />\n<a href=\"https://transparencyreport.google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransparencyreport.google.com&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=11651c73\" target=\"_blank\">https://transparencyreport.google.com</a>"},{"pid":"7dd2dc651f58305502057aa707d154b27e0610df","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:15:36.000Z","msg":"明明就講緊支那機一嚿屎<br />\n佢哋就扯去apple iOS iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37ddcb711161e9ab1f9775a6bbbfcfbf6593941","tid":432493,"uid":33730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明就講緊支那機一嚿屎<br />\n佢哋就扯去apple iOS iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班打手慣用技倆<br />\n嘈嘈下咪變左iphone vs an機世界大戰<br />\n無人再講支那oneplus"},{"pid":"e3ead2310f1e5977662e636ac5a55c5dae935cc0","tid":432493,"uid":72186,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明就講緊支那機一嚿屎<br />\n佢哋就扯去apple iOS iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪臭係<br />\n比人轉移講an 同ios做咩<br />\n根本就係講緊支那垃圾機收集資料問題<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支那垃圾機</span></span>呀<br />\n邊個再轉移視線 邊個係鬼"},{"pid":"4e9892b1f9bccde1046b44c136c868be26ff550c","tid":432493,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩廠出既手機其實一定會有後門收集資料<br />\n<br />\n夠膽講 Apple 都係!<br />\n<br />\n咁驚咪唔好用， 唔好上網添，帳戶都唔好申請，咁就唔驚比人知你身份啦!<br />\n<br />\n老老實實你當自己係邊位 ，又唔係出名，人地邊會咁得閒跟蹤你，咪ff 咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你會實行恐襲既先好出聲反駁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好打咁多字先<br />\n吠兩聲黎聽下"},{"pid":"26ff6c1d5bcc207eddc73e3de6348c09