-&gt; &lsquo;Join user experience program&rsquo;</span></strong>. The second stream is device information, which we collect to provide better after-sales support."},{"pid":"a6c7791942fca486ee803553c6187405000939f3","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>明明就講緊支那機一嚿屎<br />\n佢哋就扯去apple iOS iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班打手慣用技倆<br />\n嘈嘈下咪變左iphone vs an機世界大戰<br />\n無人再講支那oneplus</blockquote><br />\n而家真係拉到去世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而引起世界大戰嘅支那人已經消失咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d70c2d86332230b123f3bf5039d5d76f6fd742f","tid":432493,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實啲人明唔明你同意下收集你個人資料同你唔知道嘅情況下手機有 back door 嘅分別？所以再講建立 Apple account 時會收集你個人資料真係得啖笑。</blockquote><br />\n唔好自己呃自己啦，如果你唔同意佢都繼續俾你用? 呢d先係選擇</blockquote><br />\n睇返<span style=\"color: red;\">Oneplus</span> 個回覆, Join user experience program 呢樣野的確係setup部機個陣會有問你join 定唔join, 同ios setup 個陣都會問你share 唔 share information to developer (好似係咁既名), 好多人今次剩係放大收集左咩數據呢件事, 雖然呢樣野oneplus 的確係有事先問用家, 但佢完全冇講過原來係收集咁details 既數據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWe reached out to OnePlus about the analytics tracking, and the company responded with the below statement:<br />\n<br />\nWe securely transmit analytics in two different streams over HTTPS to an Amazon server. The first stream is usage analytics, which we collect in order for us to more precisely fine tune our software according to user behavior. This transmission of usage activity <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">can be turned off by navigating to &lsquo;Settings&rsquo; -&gt; &lsquo;Advanced&rsquo; -&gt; &lsquo;Join user experience program&rsquo;</span></strong>. The second stream is device information, which we collect to provide better after-sales support.</blockquote><br />\n補充一點, 佢係講左分別有兩類數據收集既, 據我推斷以上開閂機, 用咩app 個d咁details 數據係屬於第一類, 就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Join user experience program</span></strong>, 如果冇join 到呢個program 既機係無事, 第二類應該係imei 個堆數據, 佢話係to provide better after-sales support, 佢要呢d資料都算合理, 但佢呢樣野係冇得熄左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c248bfa444c567773eeb9c1b6a240c29dd0e0a97","tid":432493,"uid":105513,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"連登真係好多one plus打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f61c38788b574a154f8d4ebc7646b9603872e1d","tid":432493,"uid":23677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實啲人明唔明你同意下收集你個人資料同你唔知道嘅情況下手機有 back door 嘅分別？所以再講建立 Apple account 時會收集你個人資料真係得啖笑。</blockquote><br />\n唔好自己呃自己啦，如果你唔同意佢都繼續俾你用? 呢d先係選擇</blockquote><br />\n睇返<span style=\"color: red;\">Oneplus</span> 個回覆, Join user experience program 呢樣野的確係setup部機個陣會有問你join 定唔join, 同ios setup 個陣都會問你share 唔 share information to developer (好似係咁既名), 好多人今次剩係放大收集左咩數據呢件事, 雖然呢樣野oneplus 的確係有事先問用家, 但佢完全冇講過原來係收集咁details 既數據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWe reached out to OnePlus about the analytics tracking, and the company responded with the below statement:<br />\n<br />\nWe securely transmit analytics in two different streams over HTTPS to an Amazon server. The first stream is usage analytics, which we collect in order for us to more precisely fine tune our software according to user behavior. This transmission of usage activity <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">can be turned off by navigating to &lsquo;Settings&rsquo; -&gt; &lsquo;Advanced&rsquo; -&gt; &lsquo;Join user experience program&rsquo;</span></strong>. The second stream is device information, which we collect to provide better after-sales support.</blockquote><br />\n補充一點, 佢係講左分別有兩類數據收集既, 據我推斷以上開閂機, 用咩app 個d咁details 數據係屬於第一類, 就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Join user experience program</span></strong>, 如果冇join 到呢個program 既機係無事, 第二類應該係imei 個堆數據, 佢話係to provide better after-sales support, 佢要呢d資料都算合理, 但佢呢樣野係冇得熄左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6y7qrk4p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6y7qrk4p&h=329591af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eb9c086d367c1d3819d7b480744e936fa755a9b","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登真係好多one plus打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係多到顛<br />\n指鹿為馬，不停毒人去認同支那機偷偷哋收集個人資料係應該嘅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34563ed70e3b1b301c618388da4f30366037a96","tid":432493,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15352a47b7b1658e5e9d4c758d7041aeadd735c0","tid":432493,"uid":39527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"支那機唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c062d9704306b7ba96708349c7cb4d79cba0879a","tid":432493,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打手機時入黎講返句公道說話"},{"pid":"81688f37f00f75247e9d8ac741cd2ff86aa9b957","tid":432493,"uid":6195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"軟飯王捨得入嚟未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7697